Package: rwhy
Title: Your AI-Powered R Programming Assistant
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("fQwQf", email = "fQwQf6@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An AI assistant that lives in your R console.
    Explain errors with why(), generate code with ask_r(), and get instant
    help from large language models without ever leaving your R session.
    Supports OpenAI-compatible APIs (DeepSeek, Qwen, Kimi, etc.).
